elements.label: Streak Summary > Fire Icon
elements.description: Orange flame icon displayed prominently in the center of the screen, below the 'day streak!' text
elements.explanation: Box is well-aligned and tightly fits the fire icon, with minimal extra space.

elements.label: Streak Summary > Streak Count
elements.description: Large orange number '1' displayed above the 'day streak!' text at the center of the screen
elements.explanation: Box accurately frames the '1' streak count with appropriate margins.

elements.label: Streak Summary > Streak Label
elements.description: Orange text 'day streak!' positioned directly below the streak count number in the center of the screen
elements.explanation: Box was too large, encompassing both the count and the fire icon; resized to tightly fit the 'day streak!' label.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Day Indicator Layout
elements.description: Horizontal row of five day indicators showing weekday abbreviations (F, Sa, Su, M, Tu) inside a white rectangular container with rounded corners
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly fits the entire day indicator layout, including all five indicators and the whitespace. Very minor possible adjustment on bottom margin.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Friday Indicator
elements.description: Circle with orange checkmark labeled 'F', positioned as the leftmost indicator in the day tracker row
elements.explanation: Box is well-centered on the orange Friday indicator circle. Contains the letter and icon with slight extra space on the right.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Saturday Indicator
elements.description: Empty gray circle labeled 'Sa', positioned as the second indicator from the left in the day tracker row
elements.explanation: Box fits around the second circle and label, with slight extra space at the bottom. Alignment is visually correct.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Sunday Indicator
elements.description: Empty gray circle labeled 'Su', positioned as the middle indicator in the day tracker row
elements.explanation: Box actually duplicates the Saturday indicator's box and does not surround any unique third indicator. No valid correction as current coordinates overlap other elements.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Monday Indicator
elements.description: Empty gray circle labeled 'M', positioned as the fourth indicator from the left in the day tracker row
elements.explanation: Bounding box covers the Monday indicator accurately, with minor excess on left/right but clearly identifies the correct element.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Tuesday Indicator
elements.description: Empty gray circle labeled 'Tu', positioned as the rightmost indicator in the day tracker row
elements.explanation: Box fits the rightmost circle and label. Margins are correct; position matches visual element.

elements.label: Streak Tracker > Warning Message
elements.description: Gray text message 'But your streak will reset if you don't practice tomorrow. Watch out!' inside the white container below the day indicator circles
elements.explanation: Text bounding box fits the warning message directly under the circles. Margins above and below the text are minimal and appropriate.

elements.label: Continue Button > Button
elements.description: Bright green rectangular button with rounded corners displaying 'CONTINUE' in white uppercase text, positioned at the bottom of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely fits the green continue button including its rounded corners, with only minimal padding visible.
